view.name: DPD: Reported Major Crimes, 2011-2014
view.description: Reported major crime offenses from Jan 1, 2011 through Dec 31, 2014 for the City of Detroit.

Metadata.Disclaimer: This PRELIMINARY INFORMATION is used on an ongoing basis by the Detroit Police Department for strategic planning and crime analysis. This data is not final and thus is not the crime data that is reported to the FBI Uniform Crime Reporting Program.
